Text: Thank You!!! My first and favorite series from childhood years back again.

Never mind. Sorry. It was my stupid mistake, I hadn't reinstalled a rar program. These work just fine. Thanks for the great upload.
does anyone have Bearers of the Black Staff?

How does anybody know if they are abridged or unabridged?  The ONLY info we have is author, series name, and number of titles.  THats crazy.  Does TPB charge by word in the description box uploader? Thank you very much!!!

Torrent works perfectly. Downloaded @ 1.3MB/sec wich is max for me. Also it had nice sound quality and no viruses.

Also love the books. Worth reading(or listening to in this case) for anyone intrested in the fantasy genre.

See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shannara for more info regarding the books/author.
